    H_SIN                   "Computes the Sine of X.  Set trig (deg, rad, gra) mode in File/Settings."
    T_COS                   "Cosine"
    H_COS                   "Computes the Cosine of X.  Set trig (deg, rad, gra) mode in File/Settings."
