    H_FINPV                 "Computes the present value of money based on entries in the financial registers."
    T_FINPMT                "Periodic Payment"
    H_FINPMT                "Computes the periodic payment of a loan based on entries in the financial registers."
    T_FINFV                 "Future Value"
    H_FINFV                 "Computes the future value of money based on entries in the financial registers."
